City Court of New York — General Term, March, 1900.

Before Fitzsimons, Ch. J., and Conlan, J.

Everett Clapp, Appellant, v. William A. Cooper, Impleaded, etc., Respondent. Appeal from a judgment in favor of de-1 fendant. Henry B. Kinghom, for James P. Lowrey, for Respondent.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. No opinion.
